with cte as(SELECT indicatorvalue as GDP_growth_value,year, countryname,max(indicatorvalue) over(partition by countryname) as highest_gdp
FROM wdi_opencsv_text_view 
WHERE indicatorcode = 'NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG')
SELECT GDP_growth_value,year, countryname
FROM cte
WHERE GDP_growth_value = highest_gdp and GDP_growth_value <> 0.0
